02:31.200 --> 02:33.395
Where you at, Vinny?
I'm coming!

02:33.480 --> 02:35.118
He's coming.

02:36.440 --> 02:39.591
139 pounds
and three-quarters.

02:39.720 --> 02:40.789
Fuck.

02:41.640 --> 02:43.312
Tell Vinny that
