02:48.040 --> 02:50.838
Beating your pizza-faced,
Liberace-son back to Boston.

02:50.920 --> 02:53.878
Hey! Hey!
We're from Providence!

02:53.960 --> 02:56.997
He'll be here. He'll be here.
