02:57.080 --> 02:59.992
Don't you worry about that.
He's gonna be here. He's gonna be here.

03:36.160 --> 03:37.559
He gonna make it?

03:40.680 --> 03:42.591
Got a little
surprise for you.

03:44.640 --> 03:47.234
Get your motherfucking
dick out my face!

03:47.800 --> 03:49.472
He can't take
his eyes off me.

03:51.680 --> 03:53.318
He still looks big.

03:53.400 --> 03:55.311
This is gonna be close.

04:08.840 --> 04:10.751
140 pounds even.

04:10.840 --> 04:11.909
Yeah!

04:28.840 --> 04:31.149
Behind me,
the casino here at Caesar's,

04:31.280 --> 04:33.475
and, yes,
the eve of the big fight.

04:33.560 --> 04:37.439
Roger Mayweather defending
against Vinny Pazienza.

04:37.520 --> 04:39.670
For the WBC super
lightweight championship...

04:40.840 --> 04:41.856
Bottom line is
that I'm willing

04:41.880 --> 04:43.552
