ring tomorrow night.

04:44.040 --> 04:46.838
I don't think he's ready
to make that sacrifice.

04:46.920 --> 04:48.956
Damn straight. 'Cause
there ain 't no need to.

04:49.040 --> 04:51.270
Boy thinking about
dying instead of boxing.

04:51.360 --> 04:53.635
That should tell you
all you need to know.

04:56.400 --> 04:58.994
Motherfucker,
tomorrow night, you gone.

04:59.080 --> 05:01.071
I'm gonna rain on you
like a thunderstorm.

05:01.160 --> 05:02.309
Be scared.
Yeah.

05:02.400 --> 05:04.994
Do me a favor though, tomorrow
you get yourself a Tic Tac.

05:05.080 --> 05:06.536
And if you're this
close to me tomorrow,

05:06.560 --> 05:08.080
I'm gonna knock you the fuck out.
Okay.

05:15.960 --> 05:17.313
You all right, champ?

05:17.440 --> 05:18.873
Yeah, yeah.
I'm feeling good.

05:19.120 --> 05:20.120
Yeah.

05:21.320 --> 05:22.878
I know you are.

05:23.360 --> 05:25.191
You need anything?
Nah, I'm good.

05:25.320 --> 05:28.790
What you doing? You going to bed?
Yeah. Big day tomorrow.

05:29.760 --> 05:31.796
Hey, you should
hit the hay, too.

05:31.880 --> 05:32.880
Yeah, definitely, Pop.

05:32.920 --> 05:34.831
Okay, good night.
Good night.

05:41.640 --> 05:45.872
Ride the fever.
Wally Cleaver loves the beaver!

05:55.080 --> 05:56.559
Blow on those.

05:57.360 --> 05:58.952
Yeah!

05:59.040 --> 06:01.873
Baby. You're up 100K,
all right?

06:01.960 --> 06:03.313
Shouldn't you
just call it quits?

06:03.400 --> 06:05.436
Yeah, yeah.
Just order another OJ.

06:05.520 --> 06:06.794
I'm not thirsty.

06:12.480 --> 06:15.790
What are you doing here?
I'm splitting 10s.

06:15.880 --> 06:17.836
I mean,
don't you think you should be

06:17.920 --> 06:19.120
getting some
rest for tomorrow?

06:19.200 --> 06:21.475
It is tomorrow. Yeah, relax.
Just go ahead.

06:26.880 --> 06:28.438
Okay, yeah.

06:30.160 --> 06:31.354
I don't like this.

06:35.720 --> 06:37.870
Too many, too many! Yes!

06:38.000 --> 06:40.673
Baby, come on! Yeah, baby!
Vinny! Vinny!

06:40.760 --> 06:42.512
God, Vinny!

06:42.600 --> 06:44.989
Yeah. Yeah!
Too many!

06:45.080 --> 06:46.229
Boom!

06:46.480 --> 06:47.754
He's an animal.

07:00.080 --> 07:03.197
Who splits 10s
on a $20,000 hand?

07:03.600 --> 07:05.318
You shut up.

07:28.000 --> 07:29.797
Come on, Vinny!
Come on!

07:33.680 --> 07:35.989
Solid right hand
inside by Mayweather.

07:36.080 --> 07:38.310
Pazienza stopped
in his tracks.

07:38.400 --> 07:40.960
Got his attention
pretty good right there.

07:42.360 --> 07:43.679
What are you doing?
Get in there.

07:47.120 --> 07:49.496
- Solid right hand right on the eye!
- That hurt him.

07:49.520 --> 07:50.919
I question,
though,

07:51.000 --> 07:53.719
whether we'll ever see
Pazienza in the ring again

07:53.800 --> 07:56.394
after taking
a beating like this.

07:57.480 --> 07:59.277
That guy's
got a lot of heart.

07:59.400 --> 08:01.520
I'm telling you, he's got a lot of heart.

08:02.200 --> 08:04.873
More action after the bell.

08:05.640 --> 08:07.119
I can take that
all day!

08:07.240 --> 08:09.708
You got nothing!
Come on! Come on!

08:09.840 --> 08:11.558
I got it. I got it.
I got it. I'm fine.

08:11.640 --> 08:12.914
I got it. I got it.

08:15.080 --> 08:16.718
I got this. I got it.

08:17.400 --> 08:19.000
Darryl,
give us your score.

08:19.080 --> 08:21.230
Okay, I've got it to
eight rounds to three.

08:21.360 --> 08:23.510
107-101,
favor Roger Mayweather.

08:23.600 --> 08:25.960
I think he's winning the fight big,
and certainly the night.

08:26.520 --> 08:28.176
Good right hand right there.

08:28.200 --> 08:30.350
That was the best
right hand of the fight.

08:30.440 --> 08:32.111
Why let it go any further?

08:33.480 --> 08:35.549
Well, because he's a fighter.

08:36.919 --> 08:39.096
- Watch him finish the fight.
- Well, that's true.

08:39.120 --> 08:40.188
What's going on?

08:40.280 --> 08:42.429
Nothing, Ma.
He's still in his corner.

08:42.520 --> 08:43.936
I'm stopping that fight.

08:43.960 --> 08:46.235
I'm not waiting for a doctor
to make the decision.

08:46.320 --> 08:48.356
You're not
gonna win on points.

08:48.440 --> 08:51.398
You gotta knock him out. Vinny,
you gotta knock him out.

08:51.480 --> 08:54.153
Hey, champ.
Champ. You all right?

08:54.240 --> 08:55.880
Yeah. Yeah, I'm fine.
You all right? Okay.

08:55.960 --> 08:59.430
You got this. You got this.
Now let's bury him!

09:04.400 --> 09:06.436
Two hands, Vinny!

09:07.640 --> 09:09.676
Oh, God.

09:12.080 --> 09:13.115
Look at his arms.

10:00.200 --> 10:01.713
You have ketosis.

10:02.280 --> 10:05.317
What does that mean?
I'm just dehydrated, Pop.

10:06.080 --> 10:07.433
We're in
the desert, Vinny.

10:07.520 --> 10:10.239
I see a lot of dehydration cases.
This isn't that.

10:10.920 --> 10:14.196
Doc, I've been doing it this way forever.
This is how it goes for me.

10:14.280 --> 10:16.430
Well, you can't keep
doing it like this.

10:16.520 --> 10:18.476
Yeah. Thank you, Doc.

10:18.560 --> 10:19.709
Appreciate it.

10:27.880 --> 10:28.949
It's weird, Ma.

10:29.040 --> 10:31.634
It's not weird.
Don't put too much salt.

10:31.720 --> 10:33.176
I'm not gonna put salt,
I'm putting parsley.

10:33.200 --> 10:34.760
If you hadn't
knocked this thing over...

10:37.240 --> 10:39.216
Would you stop crying about
the fucking elephant already?

10:39.240 --> 10:40.336
All right, there we go.
Honest.

10:40.360 --> 10:41.416
I'm just sayin',
I'm not crying.

10:41.440 --> 10:43.237
Hey, you want to
set the table, Jon?

10:43.320 --> 10:44.719
Sorry.

10:45.720 --> 10:48.154
Hey, Ma.
You watch the fight, yet?

10:48.240 --> 10:50.800
No. I can't
watch you get hurt.

10:51.760 --> 10:53.990
Yeah, well,
you know I don't get hurt.

10:54.080 --> 10:55.433
Where's the tape at?

10:55.520 --> 10:57.112
It's in the VCR.

10:59.720 --> 11:00.896
Can you put
that there, please?

11:00.920 --> 11:02.176
Well, will you move
this thing off the table?

11:02.200 --> 11:04.430
I can't do two
things at once, can I?

11:07.240 --> 11:10.198
The WBC super lightweight title.

11:11.680 --> 11:14.797
If "will" and "want to" alone
was all that mattered,

11:15.160 --> 11:19.438
Pazienza could beat this guy,
but "will" would only take you so far,

11:19.520 --> 11:22.273
unless you can bring
some skill along with it.

11:22.360 --> 11:25.830
That's called an old-fashioned
paintjob in Philadelphia.

11:28.120 --> 11:32.272
And for about the half-dozenth time,
they scrimmage after the bell.

11:32.360 --> 11:35.033
And Lou Duva goes
after Roger Mayweather.

11:35.120 --> 11:38.192
Now that's one of the silliest
things he could ever have done.

11:38.280 --> 11:40.794
Well,
Mayweather punched him!

11:41.600 --> 11:43.875
We're talking about
a guy in his 60s...

11:43.960 --> 11:45.678
Vinny, shut it off!

11:45.760 --> 11:48.911
We're eating.
Okay. I'm coming.

11:53.920 --> 11:55.736
How'd it feel to take
a shot from a world champ?

11:55.760 --> 11:57.591
He hits like
a altar boy.

11:58.120 --> 12:00.816
What do you think will be the
next move for Vinny after this fight?

12:00.840 --> 12:02.736
Next. I don't know if
there's gonna be a next.

12:02.760 --> 12:04.280
Now's not the time
for an announcement,

12:04.320 --> 12:08.791
but as far as I'm concerned,
Vinny Pazienza shouldn't fight no more.

12:08.880 --> 12:11.872
Now, boxing's been good to him
and he's been good to boxing,

12:12.000 --> 12:13.136
and that's
where it should end.

12:13.160 --> 12:14.559
Excuse me, I'm sorry.

12:16.480 --> 12:18.072
I'm good. Vinny, darling,
come here.

12:18.160 --> 12:19.275
I'll have more.

12:19.520 --> 12:20.873
Ridiculous.

12:21.000 --> 12:22.376
Just be happy
with what you got.

12:22.400 --> 12:24.280
It's gonna fall out of her head now,
you know...

13:03.040 --> 13:04.758
Pop, stay calm,
all right?

13:04.840 --> 13:07.229
I need them to
set the next fight.

13:13.200 --> 13:15.270
Vinny, Angelo,
come on in.

13:19.960 --> 13:21.757
Angelo. Uh...

13:21.840 --> 13:23.319
What a surprise.

13:23.400 --> 13:24.549
How you doing, Vinny?

13:24.680 --> 13:25.795
They block
the driveway?

13:26.600 --> 13:28.158
We need to talk.

13:28.240 --> 13:29.376
You should have
called first.

13:29.400 --> 13:31.336
You know I don't like to
take meetings in the house.

13:31.360 --> 13:34.079
Yeah, and you should have thought
before opening your fucking mouth

13:34.160 --> 13:36.833
and telling the whole world
my son should retire.

13:36.960 --> 13:40.396
All right, all right, all right.
Come on, now, Lou. Let's talk.

13:41.040 --> 13:42.632
Come on.
Fine. Let's talk.

13:47.200 --> 13:49.236
Vinny ain't
done, Lou.

13:50.400 --> 13:54.871
And even if you think he is, you've
got no business announcing it on HBO.

13:54.960 --> 13:57.110
What the fuck.

13:57.200 --> 13:59.395
Vinny'll decide
when he's done.

13:59.480 --> 14:01.880
Well, I wish we'd spoken first,
but it's not a perfect world.

14:01.920 --> 14:04.718
It's fine. It's all right.
Lou, I need another fight.

14:06.240 --> 14:07.896
What's with
the deep fuckin' breath?

14:07.920 --> 14:09.831
You owe him another
fight on his contract.

14:09.920 --> 14:11.353
Pop.

14:11.440 --> 14:12.839
Lookit, Vinny.

14:12.920 --> 14:14.194
All I'm saying
is that

14:14.280 --> 14:17.041
I think maybe you ought to start
thinking about more important things.

14:17.320 --> 14:19.576
Your sister's getting married.
You should consider doing the same.

14:19.600 --> 14:20.600
Start a family.

14:20.680 --> 14:23.240
What the fuck does that have
to do with him fighting?

14:23.320 --> 14:24.320
Pop, please.

14:24.400 --> 14:26.056
Even when you win,
we end up in the hospital.

14:26.080 --> 14:28.719
Who's "we"?
I ain't never seen you there.

14:32.280 --> 14:33.315
Huh?

14:33.400 --> 14:35.550
Lou, for fuck's sake,
say something!

14:37.480 --> 14:41.268
You got heart, kid, but you
wear it on your fucking chin.

14:41.400 --> 14:43.755
I seriously think you ought
to consider hanging it up.

14:43.840 --> 14:46.957
I'm not done yet, all right?
I got more in me.

14:47.040 --> 14:49.918
That's not the problem.
You always got more.

14:51.360 --> 14:53.271
I'm begging you here, Lou.

14:53.360 --> 14:55.191
Give me another shot.

14:57.640 --> 14:58.993
Just one more.

15:53.000 --> 15:54.752
Fuck. Shit.

16:10.560 --> 16:11.754
Rough night?

16:11.840 --> 16:13.876
No. Great night.

16:13.960 --> 16:15.473
Rough morning.

16:17.760 --> 16:19.398
You're early.

16:19.480 --> 16:20.993
You're drunk.

16:21.080 --> 16:22.593
No, I'm hungover.

16:22.680 --> 16:24.716
There's a
huge difference.

16:26.160 --> 16:28.151
Well, you smell
like liquor.

16:28.240 --> 16:30.117
And you smell
like Rhode Island.

16:32.280 --> 16:33.952
What? You've never
had a big night before?

16:34.040 --> 16:35.712
No. I don't drink.

16:35.800 --> 16:36.869
Yeah?

16:36.960 --> 16:38.393
Good for you.

16:38.880 --> 16:40.920
Now, if we're done with the
fucking introductions...

16:41.000 --> 16:42.911
I can't see shit
out here.

16:53.960 --> 16:56.349
This is where you
trained Tyson, huh?

16:56.440 --> 16:57.589
Yeah.

16:57.680 --> 16:58.680
That is crazy.

17:05.640 --> 17:07.073
This your family?

17:08.200 --> 17:09.315
Yeah.

17:10.440 --> 17:12.237
You guys go
to Disneyland?

17:13.560 --> 17:15.550
World. In Orlando.

17:16.839 --> 17:18.955
Oh... Not yet.

17:20.599 --> 17:22.318
So, why did Tyson fire you?

17:24.280 --> 17:26.510
What?
Was it that DUI thing?

17:27.800 --> 17:29.995
What are you,
a newspaperman?

17:31.400 --> 17:32.799
Nah, I'm just asking.

17:33.720 --> 17:35.676
Do you not want
to be here?

17:35.760 --> 17:37.398
Yeah, I'm standing here,
aren't I?

17:39.480 --> 17:41.948
All right, listen.
Let's get real, Vinny.

17:42.640 --> 17:43.789
Yeah.

17:46.240 --> 17:49.073
You lost three in a row,
last one, a title fight,

17:49.160 --> 17:51.515
you got nothing lined up
'cause you're not a draw,

17:51.600 --> 17:55.718
your own manager, on fucking HBO,
said you should hang it up.

17:55.800 --> 17:58.712
The only reason
you're standing in my gym

17:58.800 --> 18:05.194
is because Lou sent you here
to put us both out to pasture.

18:08.200 --> 18:12.034
So, if you want to get this over
with, let's get it over with.

18:21.200 --> 18:22.553
You all set?
Yeah.

18:22.640 --> 18:24.710
All right.
This is Manny.

18:25.800 --> 18:27.313
How we doing?
How are you?

18:27.400 --> 18:28.753
You'll be sparring
with him today.

18:29.920 --> 18:31.114
Okay.

18:31.600 --> 18:33.511
How much you weigh?
190.

18:34.000 --> 18:35.831
You know that I fight
at junior welter, right?

18:35.920 --> 18:38.832
I know. Head-gear's in
the locker by the wall.

18:58.840 --> 18:59.840
Come on.

19:10.800 --> 19:12.199
That's enough!

19:12.640 --> 19:13.755
That's enough!

19:27.080 --> 19:28.911
Get on.
Why?

19:29.480 --> 19:32.278
What, "why"? Why not?
Gotta know where we're starting.

19:32.400 --> 19:34.391
I'm not in camp
or nothing.

19:34.480 --> 19:35.799
I haven't been training.

19:36.200 --> 19:37.679
Let's see.

19:37.760 --> 19:38.988
All right.

19:39.560 --> 19:40.834
There's no point.

19:40.920 --> 19:42.797
I'm gonna be way over.

19:49.800 --> 19:52.216
You just fought at 140 two weeks ago.
What, did you eat a horse?

19:52.240 --> 19:54.800
I told you,
I haven't been training.

19:54.920 --> 19:56.831
That's not what
I usually weigh.

19:59.840 --> 20:01.831
I'm not at my
fight weight right now.

20:02.840 --> 20:05.070
Hey, Vinny, I just
saw you use your weight.

20:05.720 --> 20:07.950
It wasn't
slowing you down. At all.

20:09.520 --> 20:12.478
Look, I don't need to cut corners, Kev.
I can make weight.

20:12.560 --> 20:13.834
No, maybe you're
at your weight.

20:15.160 --> 20:16.912
Cutting corners is
what you've been doing.

20:18.120 --> 20:19.240
I won my first
world title...

20:19.320 --> 20:20.320
As a lightweight, I know.

20:20.400 --> 20:22.760
The first time I got laid was
in my high school parking lot.

20:22.800 --> 20:25.917
You see me taking my wife there every
time I want to get my rocks off?

20:26.000 --> 20:27.513
Look at you.

20:27.600 --> 20:29.296
You're a different fighter,
your body's changed.

20:29.320 --> 20:31.390
You're bigger.
You hit with more power.

20:32.800 --> 20:34.313
You think I should
move up?

20:34.800 --> 20:35.800
Eh...

20:38.440 --> 20:39.475
Welterweight?

20:43.040 --> 20:44.837
Junior middle?
Are you nuts?

20:44.920 --> 20:48.276
You're outta your head, Kev. Come on.
Nobody jumps two classes.

20:48.360 --> 20:50.112
That's...
No, no, that's a huge risk,

20:50.200 --> 20:52.216
which is the exact opposite
of what everybody tells me

20:52.240 --> 20:53.514
I should be doing
right now.

20:55.680 --> 20:57.432
It's a risk.

21:00.200 --> 21:01.792
This is The Clock.

21:02.520 --> 21:05.512
He's gonna teach you
how to move and time.

21:07.280 --> 21:09.396
Jesus Christ, Kev!
What's that thing made out of?

21:09.480 --> 21:10.754
Rock maple.

21:10.840 --> 21:13.434
And you don't get to hit
The Clock back yet, neither. Not yet.

21:13.520 --> 21:15.400
I only want you
to avoid him for now, all right?

21:17.640 --> 21:19.915
Bend your knees.
Move your head.

21:20.000 --> 21:21.600
Right, left.
Move your head. Left, right.

21:21.680 --> 21:23.671
Throw a punch,
you move your head.

21:27.760 --> 21:29.239
You look like
a two-by-four.

21:38.920 --> 21:40.990
No. Come on,
Vinny. Move your head.

21:41.080 --> 21:43.116
Come on.
Look at it. Anticipate it.

21:44.360 --> 21:45.839
No. Punch, move.
Punch, move.

21:51.240 --> 21:52.593
I got this. Come on.

21:58.600 --> 21:59.794
Here we go.

22:01.000 --> 22:02.240
That's it,
that's it, that's it.

22:02.320 --> 22:04.629
On the side,
sit down on it.

22:13.480 --> 22:15.038
Bad intentions.

22:15.520 --> 22:16.589
Bad intentions.

22:18.480 --> 22:20.198
Now you're moving.
Bend your knees.

22:20.320 --> 22:22.072
Keep your hands up.
Keep your hands up.

22:22.160 --> 22:23.229
Good.

22:23.880 --> 22:26.394
You're looking good now.
You're moving your head.

22:30.280 --> 22:33.909
All right, stop. Okay, Vinny, that's good.
Vinny, Vinny! Stop!

