Be quiet, all right?

24:36.840 --> 24:38.956
And this is...
Oh, yeah, I remember.

24:39.080 --> 24:40.115
Hi, Shelly.

24:40.240 --> 24:41.275
Actually, it's Heather.

24:41.680 --> 24:43.079
Oh, I'm sorry.
