24:43.160 --> 24:44.275
Hi, Mr. Pazienza.

24:44.400 --> 24:45.549
No. Angelo.

24:45.640 --> 24:46.868
Angelo. Nice to meet you.

24:46.960 --> 24:48.951
- Hey, sweetheart.
