25:11.520 --> 25:13.078
Babe, you good?

25:13.240 --> 25:14.896
What else do you need?
No, no. I think I'm good.

25:14.920 --> 25:16.640
Everybody start with the salad.
All right...

25:21.560 --> 25:23.073
You settled in
all right?

