25:30.920 --> 25:32.797
Oh, yeah?

25:33.120 --> 25:34.439
I'm good.

25:39.640 --> 25:42.154
So, let me ask you,

25:42.240 --> 25:44.993
who told you to come in here
with your missionary bullshit

25:45.080 --> 25:47.116
and change
the whole program?

25:48.040 --> 25:50.508
