fucking move.

26:03.320 --> 26:06.517
How do you expect the Duvas
to find him a match?

26:07.680 --> 26:09.318
That's their job.

26:11.120 --> 26:13.588
Vinny made this decision,
Mr. Pazienza.

26:13.680 --> 26:16.056
I don't know why you're so worried
'cause he's a great fighter.

26:16.080 --> 26:18.469
Yeah, I know
he's a great fighter.

26:18.560 --> 26:20.198
