before he met you.

26:57.920 --> 27:00.798
All right, you be first.
You be first.

27:02.440 --> 27:03.714
There you go.

27:04.320 --> 27:05.912
All right.
That's enough.

27:06.760 --> 27:07.988
That's enough.
You tired?

27:08.080 --> 27:09.149
No, no, I'm good.

27:09.280 --> 27:10.349
Let's go one more round.

27:10.480 --> 27:12.471
Vinny, Vinny, Vinny,
that's enough.

27:13.000 --> 27:16.197
- Kev...
- Don't "Kev" me. Come on.

27:16.400 --> 27:17.833
All right.
See you tomorrow.

27:17.920 --> 27:21.913
Hey, champ, Kev, my office.
Both of youse.

27:24.520 --> 27:25.839
All right.

27:31.920 --> 27:33.148
Sit.

27:39.040 --> 27:40.519
The fight came in.

27:41.480 --> 27:42.674
Hey.

27:42.760 --> 27:45.228
And it's a fucking
title bout.

27:46.800 --> 27:48.153
Are you serious?
Yeah.

27:48.240 --> 27:51.073
Who?
It's the French guy. Deal.

27:52.120 --> 27:53.997
Dele?
Yeah, Dele. Whatever.

27:54.080 --> 27:56.753
He's back in,
with a title fight!

27:58.400 --> 28:00.356
Kev, you hear that?

28:00.440 --> 28:03.671
I got a title fight.
I got a title fight, baby!

28:03.760 --> 28:05.910
Are you kidding me?
Come on! Hey, Vinny, Vinny.

28:06.000 --> 28:08.912
Get back to work.
Get back on your game!

28:09.040 --> 28:10.632
Come on! Yeah!

28:20.520 --> 28:22.840
It's bad enough that
you're promoting both fighters,

28:22.880 --> 28:24.359
but I know you
made a deal for Dele

28:24.480 --> 28:26.056
to fight Rossi in
Europe in three months.

28:26.080 --> 28:27.593
$250K.

28:28.120 --> 28:32.511
And we both know he's only worth that
much if it's a unifying title fight.

28:33.680 --> 28:34.749
You need Vinny to lose.

28:35.880 --> 28:38.952
It's worth just as
much to us if Vinny wins.

28:39.480 --> 28:40.959
We'll make
Dele-Rossi the under-card,

28:41.040 --> 28:43.759
put Vinny in the ring
with Sugar Ray or Duran.

28:43.840 --> 28:46.274
Duran!
That's a big fucking "if".

28:50.200 --> 28:52.475
Did you buy your
tickets to Italy yet?

28:52.680 --> 28:53.680
Huh?

28:54.240 --> 28:55.673
I bet you did.

28:56.680 --> 28:58.636
Nah. It's too soon.

28:58.720 --> 29:01.393
Forget using Vinny
as a stepping stone.

29:01.480 --> 29:03.596
You're making him
a fucking doormat.

29:04.280 --> 29:06.555
We had options at 140.

29:06.920 --> 29:08.751
At 154, our hands are tied.

29:08.840 --> 29:09.936
You said you wanted a fight.

29:09.960 --> 29:12.758
Yeah, a fight.
You're sending him to the lions.

29:13.160 --> 29:15.993
And I thought he was coming here
to bring us a bottle of champagne.

29:17.200 --> 29:18.679
I just talked to Angelo.

29:18.760 --> 29:21.479
It don't sound like nobody over
there is too upset. Just you.

29:21.920 --> 29:25.959
Go home, Kev.
Relax. This is good. For who?

29:28.200 --> 29:31.829
If you didn't finish his career in Vegas,
you're doing it now.

29:32.800 --> 29:34.313
We are?

29:34.400 --> 29:35.879
We were the ones
who asked for this?

29:36.000 --> 29:38.120
We were the ones who bumped
him up two weight classes?

29:39.560 --> 29:41.440
We were the ones who wanted
to make a big splash

29:41.520 --> 29:43.988
so that the world
could know Rooney's back.

29:45.640 --> 29:47.835
This is on you, Kev.

29:54.040 --> 29:57.555
Vinnie Pazienza is hoping
to find some stability and consistency

29:57.640 --> 30:00.200
at his new 154-pound home.

30:00.880 --> 30:04.316
Vinnie Pazienza has perhaps one last
shot to win a world championship

30:04.400 --> 30:07.437
when he takes on undefeated WBA
junior middle weight champ,

30:07.520 --> 30:08.953
Gilbert Dele.

30:09.040 --> 30:10.917
When Dele won
the title in February,

30:11.040 --> 30:12.917
he cold-cocked
a helpless opponent

30:13.040 --> 30:14.234
named Carlos Elliott.

30:15.520 --> 30:19.149
Elliott left on a stretcher,
face down, with a broken jaw.

30:19.240 --> 30:21.708
Well, good news is,
he hits like a girl.

30:22.280 --> 30:24.236
The Providence Civic Center.

30:24.320 --> 30:27.153
Fighting here has been one of
Vinny Pazienza's greatest dreams

30:27.240 --> 30:29.310
since becoming
a professional boxer.

30:29.400 --> 30:31.391
Well, it's no longer a dream.

30:31.480 --> 30:34.870
Coming up, Vinny Pazienza,
the homecoming.

30:36.280 --> 30:39.829
Gilbert is cool, nice.

30:39.920 --> 30:41.990
Well, you know,
he's a very fine guy.

30:42.080 --> 30:47.074
He's a fine guy, but he's a rough,
rough, rough guy.

30:47.160 --> 30:50.038
What does that mean?
Does he got rough hands?

30:50.160 --> 30:52.040
T ell you what, my mom owns
a salon in Cranston.

30:52.120 --> 30:54.000
He can go get a manicure,
if that's the problem.

30:59.920 --> 31:06.075
Gilbert says he can kick your Italian
ass in any country you like.

31:08.920 --> 31:11.229
Yeah? Well, not this one,
Gilbert, all right?

31:11.320 --> 31:12.958
You're stepping in
front of Providence,

31:13.120 --> 31:14.758
you're stepping in
front of my people,

31:14.840 --> 31:16.319
I've worked really
hard to get here.

31:16.400 --> 31:18.516
I'm not going anywhere
without that belt.

31:28.560 --> 31:30.357
He wishes you
the best of luck.

31:42.000 --> 31:43.000
Come on.

31:53.920 --> 31:56.593
Come on, Kev, turn the music up.
I'm feeling good.

31:56.680 --> 31:59.592
I want you fresh for tomorrow.
Come on. All right. All right.

31:59.680 --> 32:00.749
Come on, Jon!

32:00.840 --> 32:03.080
What? He asked me to hold the bag.
You want me to say no?

32:06.840 --> 32:08.193
Come on, man.

32:08.320 --> 32:09.320
What?

32:10.520 --> 32:12.033
This fight...

32:13.440 --> 32:14.509
We gotta be careful.

32:14.680 --> 32:15.715
Yeah.

32:15.800 --> 32:17.336
Kev, you bumped me
up two weight classes,

32:17.360 --> 32:18.576
it's the night
before the fight,

32:18.600 --> 32:19.776
you're telling
me to be careful?

32:19.800 --> 32:20.800
No kidding.

32:24.960 --> 32:26.336
Come on, what are you
doing right now?

32:26.360 --> 32:27.696
How is this
supposed to help anybody?

32:27.720 --> 32:30.234
I could ask you the same question.
It's 9:30.

32:30.840 --> 32:32.193
I mean, come on.

32:34.720 --> 32:38.395
Kev, look. I get it.
You need this win as much as I do.

32:38.480 --> 32:40.391
You're damn right
I need this win.

32:40.960 --> 32:43.155
But this isn't about me.
It's about you!

32:43.760 --> 32:45.193
You're all in.
All the time.

32:45.280 --> 32:47.032
Scares the shit outta me.

32:47.800 --> 32:49.119
What do you
want me to do?

32:49.200 --> 32:50.856
You want me to be half in?
Want me to be a quarter in?

32:50.880 --> 32:53.096
You want me to, like, smoke a
cigarette between rounds? What?

32:53.120 --> 32:56.317
I want you to understand the difference
between a risk and a gamble.

32:56.400 --> 32:57.879
Yeah. Risk, gambles,
whatever.

32:57.960 --> 32:59.313
No, not whatever.

32:59.400 --> 33:01.868
This, what we do here,
this is calculated, okay?

33:02.000 --> 33:04.355
We weigh the odds.
We make a choice.

33:07.560 --> 33:09.551
This ain't
blackjack, Vinny.

33:11.440 --> 33:14.432
It ain't orange juice
and tit-jobs and sunglasses.

33:14.520 --> 33:15.839
This is it.

33:16.480 --> 33:17.959
This is fucking it!

33:22.920 --> 33:25.070
Do you think I'm
going to lose this fight?

33:27.960 --> 33:29.439
No.

33:30.880 --> 33:32.711
Good. Me neither.

34:15.800 --> 34:19.076
They come from
opposite ends of the spectrum.

34:19.199 --> 34:23.795
Suave, smooth gentleman from Paris,
the champion, Gilbert Dele.

34:23.880 --> 34:28.192
Going up, the blue collar fighter
from Providence, Rhode Island,

34:28.280 --> 34:29.554
Vinny Pazienza.

34:29.639 --> 34:31.239
Sarah, come on,
it's starting any minute!

35:48.440 --> 35:49.589
Come on, champ!

35:49.960 --> 35:51.552
You be first, Vinny.
You be first!

35:51.760 --> 35:53.273
He's got...

36:00.040 --> 36:01.359
Go on, Vinny!

36:01.720 --> 36:03.039
Come on, let's go.

36:04.720 --> 36:05.869
Come on, Vin.

36:22.360 --> 36:23.509
Twist off the ropes!

36:25.960 --> 36:29.316
Dele nails Pazienza upstairs.

36:29.400 --> 36:31.550
Again, again!
Push off! Push off!

36:35.720 --> 36:37.711
Get off the ropes!
Twist off the ropes, Vinny!

36:38.600 --> 36:40.113
Come on, Vinny!
What are you doing?

36:46.680 --> 36:48.079
There you go.

36:55.120 --> 36:56.120
Vin...

36:57.600 --> 36:59.795
Doreen,
why are you so quiet?

37:03.880 --> 37:05.598
Come on! Come on!
The fuck is he doing?

37:07.640 --> 37:10.916
I've been here all day. I love it.
I can do this all day, baby.

37:11.040 --> 37:12.473
I'll see you
right after this.

37:14.240 --> 37:17.437
What are you doing, champ?
Stop playing around!

37:18.160 --> 37:19.195
Come on!

37:19.320 --> 37:20.355
Give me water.

37:22.480 --> 37:24.176
This wasn't
the game plan, all right?

37:24.200 --> 37:26.156
Why are you going
toe-to-toe with this guy, huh?

37:27.000 --> 37:28.479
Hey, Vinny, look at me.

37:30.200 --> 37:33.272
You don't move and you're gonna get hurt.
You're gonna get hurt!

37:39.040 --> 37:40.976
Don't let the feelings
get the better of you, okay?

37:41.000 --> 37:43.434
You don't have to slug
with this guy, all right?

37:45.440 --> 37:46.919
What?

37:47.000 --> 37:48.069
What is it?

37:48.200 --> 37:50.270
He doesn't hit
like a girl at all.

37:50.360 --> 37:52.112
Jesus Christ.

37:53.080 --> 37:55.150
He actually hits
pretty hard.

37:55.240 --> 37:58.312
Vinny, move your head,
all right? Come on!

37:58.400 --> 38:00.550
You kick his fucking ass!

38:08.320 --> 38:10.117
There you go!

38:18.800 --> 38:20.950
There you go! There you go!
Now you're moving!

38:29.800 --> 38:31.870
Yes, baby! Yes!

38:44.040 --> 38:46.395
Stay on him!
That's it. Yes!

38:48.880 --> 38:49.915
Come on!

39:03.080 --> 39:04.513
What are you doing, Vinny?
Come on!

39:08.920 --> 39:11.275
Come on, Vinny!
Come on, finish him off!

39:18.600 --> 39:20.160
This could end
in a knockout!

39:20.360 --> 39:21.429
Go to your corner.

39:37.280 --> 39:40.636
Ma! He did it!
Ma! He just did it!

39:40.760 --> 39:42.398
He knocked him out!
He knocked him out?

39:42.480 --> 39:43.480
Oh, my God!

39:51.720 --> 39:52.914
What are you doing?

39:53.600 --> 39:54.794
Vinny!

39:55.160 --> 39:56.275
Oh, my God!

39:56.600 --> 39:57.600
Whoo!

39:57.680 --> 39:59.079
Oh, my God,
he did it!

40:02.000 --> 40:03.256
You stuck it out, Vinny.

40:03.280 --> 40:07.159
I did it with dogged determination
and persistent perseverance.

40:07.400 --> 40:09.834
I'm back on top!
How do you feel, champ?

40:09.960 --> 40:13.475
I feel like I should be on a box of
Wheaties, doing a Gatorade commercial.

40:13.640 --> 40:16.677
I feel like I should be going to
Disneyland or something, I'm just...

40:16.800 --> 40:17.994
I'm so happy!

41:22.360 --> 41:24.555
So what?
You bulk up. No big deal.

41:24.640 --> 41:25.789
It's Duran.

41:25.920 --> 41:27.896
You'll have to fight
him super middleweight.

41:27.920 --> 41:29.478
Yeah, you think
I can handle him?

41:29.560 --> 41:31.994
I'd rather you fight
where you naturally live.

41:32.080 --> 41:34.799
I don't want you to have to
starve yourself or bulk up.

41:34.880 --> 41:36.916
But, yeah,
you can handle him.

41:37.000 --> 41:39.036
"Handle him"?
He's gonna murder him.

41:39.120 --> 41:41.839
You're too fucking nervous, Kevin.
You know that?

41:41.920 --> 41:43.194
Hey. You're not
nervous enough.

41:45.360 --> 41:46.509
Yo.

41:46.640 --> 41:47.755
Hey, you got it?

41:48.080 --> 41:49.877
She's outside.
Nice!

41:50.760 --> 41:52.159
Where you going?

41:52.280 --> 41:55.272
We're just going to Dunkin'.
Grab some coffee.

41:55.360 --> 41:56.360
All right.

41:58.560 --> 42:00.357
You be back for dinner.

42:00.440 --> 42:02.120
Yeah, well, he just
got this new car, Pops.

42:02.160 --> 42:03.718
So I might be
a little late for dinner.

42:22.760 --> 42:24.671
Does this mean
we're not going to AC?

42:24.760 --> 42:26.796
Nah. Gotta be back tonight.
Let's just do Foxwoods.

42:26.880 --> 42:28.233
All right.

42:28.360 --> 42:30.396
Hey, so did you
figure out your next fight?

42:30.480 --> 42:31.993
We're gonna skip
the rematch with Dele

42:32.120 --> 42:33.712
and go in straight
to something bigger.

42:33.800 --> 42:34.915
How big?

42:35.760 --> 42:36.795
Like Duran big.

42:38.720 --> 42:40.711
Holy shit. How much?
Jimmy!

43:29.040 --> 43:31.508
Vinny. Vinny. Vinny.

43:33.200 --> 43:34.315
Vinny.

43:34.440 --> 43:35.668
Fuck!

43:36.120 --> 43:37.120
Hey.

43:37.200 --> 43:39.873
Hey! Call a
fucking ambulance!

43:53.400 --> 43:56.790
You see the way he hits now?
Like a fucking bull.

43:56.880 --> 43:58.199
Come on. Deal.

43:58.680 --> 44:00.557
You're so quiet tonight,
Anthony.

44:00.720 --> 44:02.551
I almost forgot
you were there.

44:02.960 --> 44:05.758
I came to play cards, not to hear
about your fucking kid all night.

44:05.840 --> 44:07.558
Yeah. Fuck you.

44:08.200 --> 44:11.272
Hey, Angelo,
Vinny's on TV!

44:11.360 --> 44:13.191
Jesus Christ already.

44:14.040 --> 44:16.634
Good evening.
Rhode Island's own Pazmanian Devil

44:16.720 --> 44:20.474
is in Kent County Memorial Hospital
tonight with a fractured neck.

44:20.920 --> 44:23.388
News Watch 10 has obtained
these photographs

44:23.480 --> 44:26.756
taken at the accident scene
not long after it happened.

44:26.880 --> 44:29.838
They show the car in which
Vinny Pazienza was riding

44:29.920 --> 44:31.148
as well as the other car...

44:31.680 --> 44:33.477
...here at Kent
County Hospital

44:33.600 --> 44:35.352
as friends and
family are gathering

44:35.440 --> 44:38.079
to see what actually
happened in the accident.

44:48.680 --> 44:50.033
Champ.

44:53.200 --> 44:56.033
Champ...
No, honey, he can't.

44:57.240 --> 45:00.471
They got him all drugged up
because he couldn't breathe.

45:02.120 --> 45:03.348
What happened to him?

45:04.760 --> 45:06.478
He got hit by a car.

