01:14:01.800 --> 01:14:02.835
No, I'm fine.

01:14:02.920 --> 01:14:05.229
Ma, he can't drive.
He lost his license.

01:14:05.360 --> 01:14:06.509
Vinny.

01:14:07.200 --> 01:14:08.235
Louise?

01:14:08.360 --> 01:14:09.496
There we go.
