01:14:13.200 --> 01:14:14.792
What do you mean?
No, no, no, no...

01:14:40.320 --> 01:14:42.231
Kev, what are you doing?

01:14:43.280 --> 01:14:44.474
Go upstairs.

01:14:46.720 --> 01:14:48.073
