send you back to the hospital.

01:24:58.040 --> 01:24:59.536
I don't want to be
the one to say it...

01:24:59.560 --> 01:25:00.879
Then don't.

01:25:01.000 --> 01:25:02.513
Because I worked
too hard to hear it.

01:25:02.640 --> 01:25:04.153
Vinny...

01:25:35.440 --> 01:25:38.830
...tonight, any shot of
catching the Yankees,

